WEBVTT

40:18.400 --> 40:21.200 line:80%
[Fan]

40:18.870 --> 40:20.240 line:80%
Sorry, sir!

40:20.510 --> 40:22.510 line:80%
My sister and I were
playing hide-and-seek.

40:22.510 --> 40:23.990 line:80%
You came so suddenly,

40:24.120 --> 40:26.720 line:80%
and I didn't have time to call her
out of hiding.
